### Read all users
GET http://localhost:3002/api/v2/users

### Create a new user
POST http://localhost:3002/api/v2/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "Charlie",
  "role": "admin",
  "email": "charlie@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Update a user
PUT http://localhost:3002/api/v2/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "Neeti3",
  "email": "neeti@example.com",
  "password": "pass123"
}

### DELETE a user
DELETE http://localhost:3002/api/v2/users/1
